Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA 10173): You are collecting highly sensitive personal information (National IDs). You must register your platform with the National Privacy Commission (NPC). You should never store raw pictures of user IDs on your own servers. Let the eKYC vendor hold them securely, or delete them instantly from your storage buckets once verified.\par
