\f1\u-10178?\u-8736?\f2  \f0 Structural Optimization Rules\par
Decoupled Video Track Processing: Notice that your face filters run directly inside the browser client sandbox via ARFilterSelector before sending media data. This design pattern ensures your central API servers handle zero real-time video encoding loads.\par
\par
Asynchronous Ledger Accounting: When a user tips a performer inside TipsChatBox, the active payment state hits a fast Redis Cache instantly to update the text chat view under a millisecond. The server then pushes the update down to the PostgreSQL Primary Database asynchronously to log the legal audit trail securely without choking active server threads.\par
